28\\u6307\\u5b9akey\\u3002\\u5f53\\u67e5\\u8be2\\u591a\\u4e2a\\u65f6\\uff0c\\u53ea\\u8981\\u6709\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u5b58\\u5728\\uff0c\\u5c31\\u4f1a\\u8fd4\\u56de \\uff08integer) 1\\uff1b\\u9664\\u975e\\u90fd\\u4e0d\\u5b58\\u5728\\uff0c\\u624d\\u8fd4\\u56de (integer)0\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> exists msg\\n(integer) 0\\n```\\n\\t\\n+ mset key value [key value ...]  \\n\\t\\u6279\\u91cf\\u8bbe\\u7f6e\\u952e\\u503c\\u5bf9\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> mset k1 val1 k2 val2\\n OK\\n```\\n\\n+ mget key [key ...]   \\n\\t\\u6279\\u91cf\\u53d6key\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> mget k1 k2\\n1) \\"val1\\"\\n2) \\"val2\\"\\n ```\\n \\n+ expire [key] [time]    \\n\\t\\u7ed9\\u6307\\u5b9akey\\u8bbe\\u7f6e\\u8fc7\\u671f\\u65f6\\u95f4\\uff08\\u5355\\u4f4d\\u79d2\\uff09\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> expire msg 1000\\n(integer) 1\\n```\\n\\t\\n+ setex key seconds value    \\n\\t\\u7b49\\u4ef7\\u4e8e set + expire \\u547d\\u4ee4\\u7ec4\\u5408\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> setex test 100 hello\\nOK\\n```\\n\\n+ setnx key value\\n\\t\\u5982\\u679ckey\\u4e0d\\u5b58\\u5728\\u5219set\\u521b\\u5efa\\uff0c\\u5426\\u5219\\u8fd4\\u56de0\\n\\t\\n\\t\\u7531\\u4e8e Redis \\u7684\\u5355\\u7ebf\\u7a0b\\u547d\\u4ee4\\u5904\\u7406\\u673a\\u5236\\uff0c\\u5982\\u679c\\u6709\\u591a\\u4e2a\\u5ba2\\u6237\\u7aef\\u540c\\u65f6\\u6267\\u884c setnx key value\\uff0c\\u6839\\u636e setnx \\u7684\\u7279\\u6027\\u53ea\\u6709\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u5ba2\\u6237\\u7aef\\u80fd\\u8bbe\\u7f6e\\u6210\\u529f\\uff0csetnx \\u53ef\\u4ee5\\u4f5c\\u4e3a\\u5206\\u5e03\\u5f0f\\u9501\\u7684\\u4e00\\u79cd\\u5b9e\\u73b0\\u65b9\\u6848\\uff0cRedis \\u5b98\\u65b9\\u7ed9\\u51fa\\u4e86\\u4f7f\\u7528 setnx \\u5b9e\\u73b0\\u5206\\u5e03\\u5f0f\\u9501\\u7684\\u65b9\\u6cd5\\uff1a\\n\\thttps:\\/\\/redis.io\\/docs\\/manual\\/patterns\\/distributed-locks\\/\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> setnx tmp temp\\n(integer) 1\\n```\\n\\n+ incr [key] \\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> set integer 10\\nOK\\n127.0.0.1:6379> incr integer\\n(integer) 11\\n```\\n\\n+ incrby [key] [number]\\n\\t\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> incrby integer 5\\n(integer) 16\\n```\\n\\n+ append\\n\\n+ strlen\\n\\n+ getset\\n\\n\\n\\n2. \\u5e94\\u7528\\u573a\\u666f\\n\\n\\n### Hash\\n1. \\u547d\\u4ee4\\n\\n+ hset key field value [field value ...]\\n\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hset hashKey field_1 val_1 f_2 v_2 f_3 v_3\\n(integer) 3\\n```\\n\\n+ hdel key field [field ...]\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379>hset user:1 name tom age 21\\n(integer) 2\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hdel user:1 age\\n(integer) 1\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hgetall user:1\\n1) \\"name\\"\\n2) \\"tom\\"f\\n```\\n\\n+ hget key field\\n\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hget hashKey field_1\\n\\"val_1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hget hashKey f_2\\n\\"v_2\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ hgetall  \\n\\u83b7\\u53d6\\u6240\\u6709\\u7684 field-value\\n\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hgetall hashKey\\n1) \\"field_1\\"\\n2) \\"val_1\\"\\n3) \\"f_2\\"\\n4) \\"v_2\\"\\n5) \\"f_3\\"\\n6) \\"v_3\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ hmset key field value [field value ...]  \\n\\u6279\\u91cf\\u8bbe\\u7f6e field-value\\n\\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hmset myhash f1 v1 f2 v2\\nOK\\n```\\n \\n+ hmget key field [field ...]  \\n\\u6279\\u91cf\\u83b7\\u53d6 field-value\\n\\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hmget hashKey field_1 f_2 f_3\\n 1) \\"val_1\\"\\n 2) \\"v_2\\"\\n 3) \\"v_3\\"\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hmget myhash f1 f2\\n 1) \\"v1\\"\\n 2) \\"v2\\"\\n ```\\n \\n+ hkeys key  \\nhkeys \\u547d\\u4ee4\\u5e94\\u8be5\\u53eb hfields \\u66f4\\u4e3a\\u6070\\u5f53\\uff0c\\u5b83\\u8fd4\\u56de\\u6307\\u5b9a\\u54c8\\u5e0c\\u952e\\u6240\\u6709\\u7684field\\n \\n```shell\\n127.0.0.1:6379> hkeys myhash\\n1) \\"f1\\"\\n2) \\"f2\\"\\n```\\n\\n + hvals key  \\n \\u83b7\\u53d6\\u6240\\u6709\\u7684 value\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hvals myhash\\n 1) \\"v1\\"\\n 2) \\"v2\\"\\n ```\\n + hexists key field  \\n \\u5224\\u65ad field \\u662f\\u5426\\u5b58\\u5728\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hexists myhash f1\\n (integer) 1\\n ```\\n + hlen  \\n \\u8ba1\\u7b97 field \\u7684\\u4e2a\\u6570\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hlen myhash\\n (integer) 2\\n ```\\n \\n + hrandfield key [count [WITHVALUES]]\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hrandfield hashKey 2\\n 1) \\"f_3\\"\\n 2) \\"f_2\\"\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hrandfield hashKey 2\\n 1) \\"field_1\\"\\n 2) \\"f_2\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + hscan key cursor [MATCH pattern] [COUNT count]\\n \\n + hsetnx key field value\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hsetnx myhash f1 v1\\n (integer) 0\\n ```\\n \\n + hstrlen key field\\n \\n ```shell\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> hstrlen myhash f2\\n (integer) 2\\n ```\\n \\n + hincrby key field increment  \\n \\n\\n2. \\u5e94\\u7528\\u573a\\u666f\\n\\n### List\\n1. \\u547d\\u4ee4\\n\\n + lpush key value [value ...]  \\n \\u5c06\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u6216\\u591a\\u4e2a `value` \\u63d2\\u5165\\u5230\\u5217\\u8868 `key` \\u7684\\u8868\\u5934\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lpush mylist v1 v2 v3\\n(integer) 3\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 -1\\n1) \\"v3\\"  # \\u8868\\u5934\\n2) \\"v2\\"\\n3) \\"v1\\"  # \\u8868\\u5c3e\\n ```\\n \\n + rpush key value [value ...]  \\n \\u5c06\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u6216\\u591a\\u4e2a `value` \\u63d2\\u5165\\u5230\\u5217\\u8868 `key` \\u7684\\u8868\\u5c3e\\uff08\\u6700\\u53f3\\u8fb9\\uff09\\n\\n```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> rpush mylist v4\\n (integer) 4\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 -1\\n 1) \\"v3\\"  # \\u8868\\u5934\\n 2) \\"v2\\"\\n 3) \\"v1\\"\\n 4) \\"v4\\"  # \\u8868\\u5c3e\\n ```\\n \\n + lset key index value\\n \\n ```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lset mylist 3 v0\\n OK\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 3\\n 1) \\"v3\\"\\n 2) \\"v2\\"\\n 3) \\"v1\\"\\n 4) \\"v0\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + lindex key index\\n \\n ```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lindex mylist 3\\n\\"v0\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lindex mylist 0\\n\\"v3\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + rpop key [count]\\n \\n ```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> rpop mylist\\n\\"v0\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 3\\n1) \\"v3\\"\\n2) \\"v2\\"\\n3) \\"v1\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + lpop key [count]\\n \\n ```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lpop mylist\\n\\"v3\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 3\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v1\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + linsert key BEFORE|AFTER pivot element\\n \\n ```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 3\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v3\\n(integer) 3\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 3\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v3\\"\\n3) \\"v1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v4\\n(integer) 4\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v4\\n(integer) 5\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 5\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v3\\"\\n3) \\"v4\\"\\n4) \\"v4\\"\\n5) \\"v1\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + lrem key count element\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v3\\n(integer) 6\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v3\\n(integer) 7\\n127.0.0.1:6379> linsert mylist before v1 v3\\n(integer) 8\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 9\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v3\\"\\n3) \\"v4\\"\\n4) \\"v4\\"\\n5) \\"v3\\"\\n6) \\"v3\\"\\n7) \\"v3\\"\\n8) \\"v1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrem mylist 3 v3\\n(integer) 3\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 9\\n1) \\"v2\\"\\n2) \\"v4\\"\\n3) \\"v4\\"\\n4) \\"v3\\"\\n5) \\"v1\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + lindex key index\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> lindex mylist 0\\n\\"v2\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + llen key\\n\\n```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> llen mylist\\n (integer) 5\\n ```\\n \\n + ltrim key start stop\\n \\n ```\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 9\\n 1) \\"v2\\"\\n 2) \\"v4\\"\\n 3) \\"v4\\"\\n 4) \\"v3\\"\\n 5) \\"v1\\"\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> ltrim mylist 0 3\\n OK\\n 127.0.0.1:6379> lrange mylist 0 9\\n 1) \\"v2\\"\\n 2) \\"v4\\"\\n 3) \\"v4\\"\\n 4) \\"v3\\"\\n ```\\n \\n + blpop key [key ...] timeout\\n \\n ```\\n ```\\n \\n + brpop\\n\\n```\\n```\\n \\n + brpoplpush\\n \\n ```\\n ```\\n\\n2. \\u5e94\\u7528\\u573a\\u666f\\n\\n### Set\\n1. \\u547d\\u4ee4\\n\\n+ sadd key member [member ...]\\n\\t\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> sadd myset \\"s1\\" \\"s2\\" \\"s3\\"\\n(integer) 3\\n127.0.0.1:6379> sadd myset \\"s1\\"\\n(integer) 0\\n```\\n\\t\\n+ spop key [count]\\n\\t\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> smembers myset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s2\\"\\n3) \\"s1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> spop myset\\n\\"s1\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ srandmember key [count]\\n\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> sadd myset \\"s1\\" \\"s2\\" \\"s3\\"\\n(integer) 1\\n127.0.0.1:6379> srandmember myset\\n\\"s1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> srandmember myset -2\\n1) \\"s2\\"\\n2) \\"s2\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> srandmember myset -2\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s1\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ srem key member [member ...]\\n\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> smembers myset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s1\\"\\n3) \\"s2\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> srem myset s2\\n(integer) 1\\n127.0.0.1:6379> smembers myset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s1\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ smove source destination member\\n\\t\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> smembers myset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> smove myset yourset s3\\n(integer) 1\\n127.0.0.1:6379> smembers yourset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ scard key\\n\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> sadd myset s1 s2 s3 s4\\n(integer) 3\\n127.0.0.1:6379> scard myset\\n(integer) 4\\n```\\n\\n+ smembers key\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> smembers myset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s4\\"\\n3) \\"s2\\"\\n4) \\"s1\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ sscan key cursor [MATCH pattern] [COUNT count]\\n\\n```\\n\\t\\n```\\n\\n+ sinter key [key ...]\\n\\n```\\n127.0.0.1:6379> smembers yourset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s2\\"\\n3) \\"s1\\"\\n127.0.0.1:6379> sinter myset yourset\\n1) \\"s3\\"\\n2) \\"s2\\"\\n3) \\"s1\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ sinterstore destination key [key ...]\\n\\t\\n```\\n```\\n\\n+ sunion key [key ...]\\n\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> sunion myset yourset\\n1) \\"s1\\"\\n2) \\"s2\\"\\n3) \\"s4\\"\\n4) \\"s3\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ sunionstore destination key [key ...]\\n\\n```\\n```\\n\\n+ sdiff key [key ...]\\n\\n```\\n\\t127.0.0.1:6379> sdiff myset yourset\\n1) \\"s4\\"\\n```\\n\\n+ sdiffstore destination key [key ...]\\n\\n```\\n\\t\\n```\\n\\t\\n2. \\u5e94\\u7528\\u573a\\u666f\\n\\n### Sort Set\\n1. \\u547d\\u4ee4\\n\\t\\n+ zadd key [NX|XX] [GT|LT] [CH] [INCR] score member [score member ...]  \\n\\t\\u5c06\\u4e00\\u4e2a\\u62